verses.text:
'Tis love that makes us hap-py, 'Tis love that smooths the way;
This world is full of sor-row, Of sick-ness, death and sin;
But love will drive out trou-ble, And peace will en-ter in.

And then our hearts are hap-py, And life seems all too brief;
And joy comes to our spir-its, God is love; were his lit-tle chil-dren,
Of Je-sus and his love. God is love; we should be like him.
